title: Dani Pedrosa wins Japan Grand Prix, Rossi second
text: Oct. 11, 2015 | 10:18 AM Dani Pedrosa wins Japan Grand Prix, Rossi second Winner Dani Pedrosa, center, of Spain, second placed Valentino Rossi , left, of Italy and third placed Jorge Lorenzo of Spain listen to Spain's national anthem during the awarding ceremony of MotoGP Japanese Motorcycle Grand Prix at Twin Ring Motegi circuit in Motegi, north of Tokyo, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. (AP Photo/Shizuo Kambayashi)
